    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear what youre saying about statistics but it felt way different than just luck. it felt like a hiccup. like the world didn't load correctly for a second. if it was just coincidence i wouldn't feel this... glitchy feeling in my head. if everything is just data, wouldn't it make sense that the system would try to optimize by reusing the same character models to save on processing power?",
